@node Install "Installation"
                                 @{b}Installation@{ub}
                                ==============
    Use TMPSetup To Install or UnInstall

            or
             
            Shell:>TMPSetup or Open it by the Icon.

    
            or

    By Hand:> 
             Copy TMPRun To Sys:Wbstartup/
             Copy TMPrefs To Sys:Prefs/
         
    TMPlus Comes With>
            TMPRun
            TMPrefs
            TMPSetup

? Keep all the files above, In Same Drawer When Installing  
             
@endnode

@node usage "usage"

      Usage

1>    Install TMP First.

2>    Then Open Sys:Prefs/TMPrefs.     

3>    While TMPPrefs Runing Goto Sys/Utulities/MultiView Grab it & Drop it In, 
      TMPrefs WinDow then Goto Add & Save your First Menu From The TMPPrefs Menu.   

      After You Saved Then Quit TMPrefs & Restart Your Computer Or Open 
      Sys:WbStartup/TMPrun.


      Thats All Easy of Use Very Simple.   

@endnode

